summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2736 for the improvement of Lot Eighteen (18), Block Eighteen (18), except portion taken for Duwamish Waterway, Joseph R. McLaughlin's Waterfront Addition to The City of Seattle, and certain other property in The City of Seattle, all in the City of Seattle, by filling the same as a sanitary measure under Ordinance No. 32450, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
